children.text: Hi, and thank you for taking a few minutes to support
Therapair
— a non-profit initiative by
Unison Mental Health
We're developing a system that helps people find the right therapist through personality, values, and lived-experience alignment.
You may have seen our basic sandbox demo — it's just a starting point. We need to make the questions much more sophisticated to create truly personalised connections.
This short
5–7 minute survey
explores:
What questions matter most for matching
How many questions people will actually answer
What level of personalisation feels right
What options resonate most
Your feedback will help shape a more ethical, inclusive, and human-centred platform.
What's your profession?
Please specify your profession:
How many years have you been practising?
What type of clients do you primarily support?
(Select all that apply)
If you selected 'Other' for client types, please specify:
What therapy modalities do you mainly use?
(Select all that apply)
If you selected 'Other' for therapy modalities, please specify:

labels.placeholder: e.g., Music Therapy, Play Therapy, etc.

children.text: How do clients typically find you?
(Select all that apply)
If you selected 'Other' for how clients find you, please specify:

labels.placeholder: e.g., University clinic, Private practice network, etc.

children.text: In your experience, what makes a great match?

items.content: Shared experience of a diagnosis (ADHD, Autism, OCD, Addiction, etc)

children.text: If you selected 'Other' for great match factors, please specify:
What is the biggest challenge you face in finding clients who you are well suited for?
Do you currently screen clients for fit before accepting them?
Would you be open to sharing your own personality traits, values, and lived experiences to help clients find the right match?
Which of these attributes would create the deepest personalisation?
If you selected 'Other' for important attributes, please specify:
Would you be willing to take a personality test such as the Big Five Inventory or HEXACO?
What would you consider too personal to share?
(keeping in mind that details of your profile are never shared with the client, they are only used as a tool to correctly pair the therapist with the client using the search feature.)
If you selected 'Other' for too personal information, please specify:
How detailed should therapist profiles be?

items.content: 10 - Very detailed (a full understanding of you as a therapist and as a person)

children.text: How much time would you be willing to spend on onboarding?

items.content: As long as it takes to get the best matches with clients

children.text: Would you be interested in a one-year free listing on Therapair when we launch?
Can we contact you for future research and updates?
If you'd like updates, please provide your email:
Any additional comments or suggestions?
Thank you so much for your time and insights!
Your feedback will directly shape how we build
Therapair.com.au
If you're interested in the free listing, we'll reach out when we're ready to launch.
